<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在王座室里，仆人吹响了喇叭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王、王后驾到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都向他们鞠躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。”汤姆小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后坐在了王座上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后拿着一本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，糟糕！我的皇家书签不见了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站成一排！魔法师们！”德克厉声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向国王和王后鞠躬，说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“魔法师们现在会施展他们最擅长的魔法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊。”汤姆咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我做好准备了，猫咪。”他小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克带着一个女孩儿走到国王和王后那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的女儿，她叫安。”德克自豪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安鞠了个躬，然后挥动了魔杖。 噗!</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几十只美丽的白鸟出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后鼓起掌来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，所有其他的魔法师都施展了自己的魔法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后轮到汤姆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尊敬的陛下。”汤姆鞠了个躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很高兴见到——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿嚏！”王后突然大声打了个喷嚏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿嚏！”王后又打了个喷嚏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王皱起了眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的！”他说，“你还好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请您，”汤姆说，“用我的手帕吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手伸进了口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但汤姆没有拿出他的手帕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出了……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猫！”王后尖叫道。“阿嚏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猫？”国王跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宫里禁止养猫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>